c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0111i M\u1ef9 uy t\u00edn t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HCM\">Iso Logistics l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0111i M\u1ef9 uy t\u00edn t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HCM<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Vay_chuyen_phat_di_My_thuong_gap_nhung_kho_khan_gi\"><\/span>V\u1eady chuy\u1ec3n ph\u00e1t \u0111i M\u1ef9 th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n g\u00ec ?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Khi h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n sang M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i khai th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c h\u1ea3i quan ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. Khi b\u1ea1n g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng sang M\u1ef9, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng g\u00ec, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u1ec1u hay \u00edt \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng quan. Th\u1eddi gian th\u00f4ng quan nhanh hay ch\u1eadm n\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi gian v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn tay kh\u00e1ch. Do \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n vi\u1ec7c khai th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c h\u1ea3i quan n\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<li>C\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00ed v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n cao: g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng sang M\u1ef9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean c\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t cao. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i k\u00e8m theo \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Do \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng ty \u0111\u1ed9n gi\u00e1 cao l\u00ean so v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/li>\n<li>Th\u1eddi gian v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh: v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e0ng sang M\u1ef9 nhanh hay ch\u1eadm ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft c\u1ee7a chuy\u1ebfn bay, th\u1eddi gian th\u00f4ng quan l\u00e2u hay ch\u1eadm,\u2026. Do \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eddi gian v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1edbm h\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ban \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1506 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/njhakca-768x484-1-300x189.png\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng \u0111i M\u1ef9 2021\" width=\"433\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/njhakca-768x484-1-300x189.png 300w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/njhakca-768x484-1-640x403.png 640w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/njhakca-768x484-1-400x252.png 400w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/njhakca-768x484-1-367x231.png 367w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/njhakca-768x484-1.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 433px) 100vw, 433px\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0ng kh\u1eaft khe: b\u1edfi v\u00ec v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i n\u00ean khi g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng, kh\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i sao cho \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n, m\u00e0 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed. Chi ti\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o <a href=\"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/cach-thuc-tinh-trong-luong-khi-gui-chuyen-phat-nhanh-di-nuoc-ngoai\/\">t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_luu_y_khi_muon_gui_hang_hoa_toi_My_tai_Iso_Logistics\"><\/span>Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 t\u1ea1i Iso Logistics.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o g\u00f3i h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn tay kh\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n, nguy\u00ean v\u1eb9n v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u sau :<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng: B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra k\u0129 l\u1ea1i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u1ea1n g\u1eedi c\u00f3 n\u1eb1m trong danh m\u1ee5c h\u00e0ng c\u1ea5m hay kh\u00f4ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o anh to\u00e0n khi v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ph\u00ed.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1466 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/thieu-xe-300x167.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng \u0111i M\u1ef9 2021\" width=\"357\" height=\"199\" srcset=\"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/thieu-xe-300x167.jpg 300w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/thieu-xe-1024x571.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/thieu-xe-768x428.jpg 768w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/thieu-xe-640x357.jpg 640w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/thieu-xe-400x223.jpg 400w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/thieu-xe-367x205.jpg 367w, https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/thieu-xe.jpg 1148w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 357px) 100vw, 357px\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Trong khi g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng: b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn, \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 nh\u00e0, t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, bang, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn. Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1n th\u1eadt c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p h\u00e0ng b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c, ho\u1eb7c giao sai \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, th\u1eddi gian l\u01b0u kho s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 1 th\u00e1ng.<\/li>\n<li>Sau khi g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng : b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00ean h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng <a href=\"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/\">Iso Logistics.vn<\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tracking number. Sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9ng m\u00e3 tracking n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i ti\u1ebfn tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn khi kh\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3i h\u00e0ng m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u1eedi.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Iso_Logistics_la_dia_chi_van_chuyen_quoc_te_va_di_My_uy_tin_tai_Ha_Noi_va_HCM\"><\/span>Iso Logistics l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0111i M\u1ef9 uy t\u00edn t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HCM<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, Iso Logistics l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n uy t\u00edn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Th\u1eddi gian v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n \u0111i M\u1ef9 nhanh ch\u00f3ng, ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 7-14 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a nguy\u00ean v\u1eb9n nh\u01b0 ban \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, c\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00ed v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e0ng \u0111i M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a <strong><a href=\"\/\">ISO Logistics<\/a><\/strong> r\u1ebb, c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ty ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1edbi, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng \u0111i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong vi\u1ec7c v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro, kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1506,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1504","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-chuyen-nganh"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1504"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1504"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1504\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":6697,"href":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1504\/revisions\/6697"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1506"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1504"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","e